text: Kampong Bukit Puan (Malay for Bukit Puan Village) is a village in Belait District, Brunei, within the mukim of Labi. The postcode for Kampong Bukit Puan is KE1137. == See also == * List of villages in Brunei == References == Bukit Puan Category:Populated places in Brunei
title: Kampong Bukit Puan
